          <li><strong>Reduced excess inventory to 2%</strong> by end of Q4 2024 (against total stockholding of 12%, of which 10% safety stock)</li>
          <li><strong>Reduced paid-media CPC by 18%</strong> via BI-led launch targeting</li>
          <li><strong>Achieved launch success rates of 84% (Nov 2024) and 54% (Dec 2024)</strong> — defined as 50+ units sold within 30 days of launch</li>
